   Cron Improvements with PHP-FPM in WordPress 5.1

   A new change in 5.1 Beta 1 introduces a change in behaviour for cron
   spawning on servers running fastcgi and PHP 7.0.16+. When available,
   requests to wp-cron.php will now return a repsonse immediately, before
   processing lengthy cron jobs, allowing the request that spawned the
   cron process to end without blocking regardless of the transport method
   â€¦ Continue reading Cron Improvements with PHP-FPM in WordPress 5.1
